Description: HTTP/JSON service for listing and managing Linux processes
 Procster is a small HTTP service and CLI utility for exposing Linux
 process information as JSON.
 .
 It can return flat process listings and process trees, and also supports
 terminating processes by PID. It is intended for local or intranet-style
 administration and automation.
